    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>Enable networking</h2>

<p>append to /etc/rc.conf</p>

<pre><code>eth0="dhcp"
INTERFACE=(eth0)
ROUTES=(!gateway)
</code></pre>

<p>run command "/etc/rc.d/network restart"</p>

<h2>Enable pacman repo</h2>

<p>append to "/etc/pacman.conf"</p>

<pre><code>SigLevel=Optional TrustAll 
</code></pre>

<p>uncomment the repo in "/etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist"</p>

<h2>Upgrade</h2>

<pre><code>pacman -Syu
</code></pre>
